data.description: Discover an exquisite gem nestled in the hear of Milton - a stunning Northwest Contemporary home sure to capture your heart. Spacious, open floor plan boasts 4b/3bath, a main-level bedroom & bath for added convenience. The primary bedroom is your sanctuary, complete w/a luxurious 5-piece bath & a roomy walk-in closet. You'll be greeted by stylish tile flooring that draws into the synchronized kitchen counter-top. Plus an array of premium features, including stainless steel appliances, elegant quartz countertops, & smart plumbing. Both Beautiful & intelligent, this home boasts SMART wiring. Step onto your patio w/ Trex deck & fully fenced backyard. You'll be steps away from interurban trail, w/ endless recreational opportunities.
